      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/idx.jpg"><a id="more"></a><h1 id="環境與工具"><a href="#環境與工具" class="headerlink" title="環境與工具"></a>環境與工具</h1><ul><li><a href="https://www.noip.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NO-IP服務</a></li><li>XAMPP</li><li>TP-LINK wifi分享器改dd-wrt</li></ul><h1 id="開始"><a href="#開始" class="headerlink" title="開始"></a>開始</h1><h2 id="NO-IP設定"><a href="#NO-IP設定" class="headerlink" title="NO-IP設定"></a>NO-IP設定</h2><ul><li>申請帳號<br><a href="https://www.noip.com/sign-up" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.noip.com/sign-up</a><img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_002.jpg"></li><li>登入<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_003.jpg"></li><li>新增網址<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_004.jpg"></li><li>下載並安裝DUC<br><a href="https://www.noip.com/download?page=win" target="_blank" rel="noopener">載點</a></li><li>開啟後登入<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_005.jpg"></li><li>選擇剛剛新增的網址<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_006.jpg"></li><li>確認狀態<br>三個綠色打勾代表正常<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_007.jpg"></li></ul><h2 id="XAMPP"><a href="#XAMPP" class="headerlink" title="XAMPP"></a>XAMPP</h2><h3 id="確認PORT"><a href="#確認PORT" class="headerlink" title="確認PORT"></a>確認PORT</h3><img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_001.jpg"><h2 id="dd-wrt設定"><a href="#dd-wrt設定" class="headerlink" title="dd-wrt設定"></a>dd-wrt設定</h2><ul><li>ipconfig確認ip<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_008.jpg"></li><li>開啟wifi設定(192.168.1.1)</li><li>DDNS設定<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_009.jpg"></li><li>Port Forwarding<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_010.jpg"></li><li>DMZ<img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_011.jpg"></li></ul><h1 id="測試"><a href="#測試" class="headerlink" title="測試"></a>測試</h1><p>ping<br>  <img src="/2018/09/15/No-IP-dd-wrt-XAMPP架站/pic_013.jpg"></p><h1 id="後記"><a href="#後記" class="headerlink" title="後記"></a>後記</h1><p>純粹記步驟，稍有缺漏就會很麻煩。</p>]]></content>
      
      
